videos.description: Kaleb Johnson has other ideas for Jalen Brunson's layup attempt and Jagan Mosely capitalizes on the other end with an easy floater.
videos.headline: Hoyas' swat leads to transition floater

videos.description: Mikal Bridges swats Antwan Walker's layup and Villanova moves quickly down the court leading to Phil Booth knocking down a triple plus the foul.
videos.headline: Booth has chance for 4 after Bridges' big block

videos.description: Eric Paschall completely denies Marcus Derrickson's attempt and Mikal Bridges drains a three on the other end.
videos.headline: Paschall blocks, Bridges drains
